name: NOT IN MY BACKYARD
description:
NOT IN MY BACKYARD is a 3D top-down shooter where in you have to defend against the waves of spiders. Run, shoot and kill. Do your best to stay alive and go for the highest score!

- This project is still in active development 

- I'm adding more features; stats, upgrades, settings , etc.

- Will soon be downloadable for windows platform

- I might turn this into a mobile game and publish it on Google Play Store
